sources.description:
Cat 8 PART ONE: When an accident sends a solar flare four times larger than Earth plunging toward the planet, Military scientist Dr. Jane Brandt calls upon the one man who can possibly reverse the cataclysm: a government outsider and renegade ad-hoc scientist. He’ll have to work fast, as in a matter of hours, the planet’s atmosphere will ignite and the countdown to the end of the world will begin.
